{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/hello","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 300px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"gatsby astronaut\"\n        title=\"gatsby astronaut\"\n        src=\"/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/5a46d/gatsby-astronaut.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/1db73/gatsby-astronaut.png 75w,\n/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/8a4e8/gatsby-astronaut.png 150w,\n/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/5a46d/gatsby-astronaut.png 300w,\n/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/fc2a6/gatsby-astronaut.png 450w,\n/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/0a47e/gatsby-astronaut.png 600w,\n/static/6d91c86c0fde632ba4cd01062fd9ccfa/5a190/gatsby-astronaut.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\nHello, ini adalah blog pertama saya yang dibangun dengan GatsbyJs(graphql + react dll) + Github Pages.<br>\nselebihnya blog ini akan berisi cerita (karangan/beneran) dan tutorial.<br>\n<br>\nkarena masih tahap pengembangan,kalian bisa email ke saya jika ingin membantu pengembangan atau bisa juga mengirim cerita kalian ke blog ini.<br>\n<br>\nfadhelijlalfalah@gmail.com<br>\n<br>\nSee ya!</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 12, 2020","path":"/hello","title":"My First Post"}}},"pageContext":{}}}